"Tip-up town" is where all the perch are. Quite a few walleye and pike mixed in too. Most if those huts are in 23-25 feet of water. My hut is on the outside edge in 28 feet.
LOL Tip up town. Is that after the tip up stick,or the tip up bottle? LOL  I will say one thing,you guys have lots of ice up there.
It's a fun little community.  I've puked down a few holes there in my crazier days!  To much info?
It's a fun little community.  I've puked down a few holes there in my crazier days!  To much info? In Tip-up town, they call that Tipping-down.
Anywhere else it's referred to as chumming the hole
